								<a name="content"></a><p class="lead">Now that you have the terms for the basic computer hardware in front of you, let&#39;s learn about <strong>booting up</strong>, <strong>user interface</strong>, and other meanings for <strong>desktop</strong> and <strong>mouse</strong>.</p> 
